WITH CONTARGET_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    qtz_member_id,
    POS.qtz_receipt_id,
    case
      when COUPON.qtz_receipt_id IS NULL then 0
      else 1
    end as coupon_flg
  FROM
    prd_public.public.dmp_id_pos POS
      LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_receipt_id
        FROM
          prd_delta.qtz_s3_etl.fm_coupon_pos
        WHERE
          dt between '20240418' and '20250417'
          and coupon_category in ('01', '03', '04', '05', '06', '08', '09')
      ) COUPON
        ON POS.qtz_receipt_id = COUPON.qtz_receipt_id
  WHERE
    dt between '20240418' and '20250417'
    AND retail = '1'
),
CONTARGET_SRC_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    POS.qtz_member_id,
    qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONTARGET_POS POS
),
CONTARGET_DEST_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    POS.qtz_member_id,
    qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONTARGET_POS POS
),
CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    qtz_member_id,
    POS.qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONTARGET_SRC_POS POS
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT
          qtz_receipt_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_POS
        WHERE
          1 = 1
          AND qtz_item_id in (
            '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
          )
      ) RECEIPT
        ON POS.qtz_receipt_id = RECEIPT.qtz_receipt_id
),
CONCURRENT_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    qtz_member_id,
    POS.qtz_receipt_id,
    case
      when COUPON.qtz_receipt_id IS NULL then 0
      else 1
    end as coupon_flg
  FROM
    prd_public.public.dmp_id_pos POS
      LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_receipt_id
        FROM
          prd_delta.qtz_s3_etl.fm_coupon_pos
        WHERE
          dt between '20240418' and '20250417'
          and coupon_category in ('01', '03', '04', '05', '06', '08', '09')
      ) COUPON
        ON POS.qtz_receipt_id = COUPON.qtz_receipt_id
  WHERE
    dt between '20240418' and '20250417'
    AND retail = '1'
),
CONCURRENT_SRC_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    POS.qtz_member_id,
    qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_POS POS
),
CONCURRENT_DEST_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    POS.qtz_member_id,
    qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_POS POS
),
CONCURRENT_SRC_ITEM_POS as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name,
    qtz_member_id,
    POS.qtz_receipt_id,
    coupon_flg
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS POS
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT
          qtz_receipt_id
        FROM
          CONCURRENT_SRC_POS
        WHERE
          1 = 1
          AND qtz_item_id in (
            '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
          )
      ) RECEIPT
        ON POS.qtz_receipt_id = RECEIPT.qtz_receipt_id
),
TARGET_ITEM as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_POS
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_name,
    qtz_item_id,
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    retail_item_category_l_name
),
SRC_MEMBER_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
),
SRC_MEMBER_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
),
SRC_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    qtz_item_id,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  GROUP BY
    qtz_item_id
),
SRC_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    qtz_item_id,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    qtz_item_id
),
SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  WHERE
    1 = 1
    AND qtz_item_id not in (
      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
    )
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_s_name
),
SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  WHERE
    1 = 1
    AND qtz_item_id not in (
      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
    )
    AND coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_s_name
),
SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  WHERE
    1 = 1
    AND qtz_item_id not in (
      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
    )
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_m_name
),
SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    count(distinct SRC.qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_SRC_POS SRC
      INNER JOIN (
        SELECT distinct
          qtz_member_id
        FROM
          CONTARGET_SRC_ITEM_POS
      ) DEST
        ON SRC.qtz_member_id = DEST.qtz_member_id
  WHERE
    1 = 1
    AND qtz_item_id not in (
      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
    )
    AND coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_m_name
),
DEST_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    qtz_item_id,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  GROUP BY
    qtz_item_id
),
DEST_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    qtz_item_id,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    qtz_item_id
),
DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_s_name
),
DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_s_name,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_s_name
),
DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_m_name
),
DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    retail_item_category_m_name,
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONCURRENT_DEST_POS SRC
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
  GROUP BY
    retail_item_category_m_name
),
DEST_MEMBER_COUNT as (
  SELECT
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONTARGET_DEST_POS
),
DEST_MEMBER_COUNT_COUPON as (
  SELECT
    count(distinct qtz_member_id) as member_count
  FROM
    CONTARGET_DEST_POS
  WHERE
    coupon_flg = 0
)
SELECT
  *
FROM
  (
    (
      (
        SELECT
          *
        FROM
          (
            SELECT
              COALESCE(member_count, 0) as src_purchasers
            FROM
              SRC_MEMBER_COUNT
          )
            CROSS JOIN (
              SELECT
                COALESCE(member_count, 0) as dest_purchasers
              FROM
                DEST_MEMBER_COUNT
            )
            CROSS JOIN (
              SELECT
                ITEM.retail_item_name as retail_item_name,
                ITEM.qtz_item_id as retail_item_id,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name as retail_item_category_s_name,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name as retail_item_category_m_name,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_l_name as retail_item_category_l_name,
                case
                  when
                    ITEM.qtz_item_id in (
                      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
                    )
                  then
                    1
                  else 0
                end as target_item_flg,
                0 as coupon_flg,
                COALESCE(SRC_ITEM.member_count, 0) as other_item_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(SRC_S.member_count, 0) as category_s_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(SRC_M.member_count, 0) as category_m_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_ITEM.member_count, 0) as other_item_dest_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_S.member_count, 0) as other_category_s_dest_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_M.member_count, 0) as other_category_m_dest_purchasers
              FROM
                TARGET_ITEM ITEM
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT SRC_ITEM
                    ON ITEM.qtz_item_id = SRC_ITEM.qtz_item_id
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT SRC_S
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name = SRC_S.retail_item_category_s_name
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT SRC_M
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name = SRC_M.retail_item_category_m_name
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT DEST_ITEM
                    ON ITEM.qtz_item_id = DEST_ITEM.qtz_item_id
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT DEST_S
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name = DEST_S.retail_item_category_s_name
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT DEST_M
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name = DEST_M.retail_item_category_m_name
            )
      )
      UNION ALL
      (
        SELECT
          *
        FROM
          (
            SELECT
              COALESCE(member_count, 0) as src_purchasers
            FROM
              SRC_MEMBER_COUNT_COUPON
          )
            CROSS JOIN (
              SELECT
                COALESCE(member_count, 0) as dest_purchasers
              FROM
                DEST_MEMBER_COUNT_COUPON
            )
            CROSS JOIN (
              SELECT
                ITEM.retail_item_name as retail_item_name,
                ITEM.qtz_item_id as retail_item_id,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name as retail_item_category_s_name,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name as retail_item_category_m_name,
                ITEM.retail_item_category_l_name as retail_item_category_l_name,
                case
                  when
                    ITEM.qtz_item_id in (
                      '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
                    )
                  then
                    1
                  else 0
                end as target_item_flg,
                1 as coupon_flg,
                COALESCE(SRC_ITEM.member_count, 0) as other_item_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(SRC_S.member_count, 0) as category_s_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(SRC_M.member_count, 0) as category_m_src_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_ITEM.member_count, 0) as other_item_dest_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_S.member_count, 0) as other_category_s_dest_purchasers,
                COALESCE(DEST_M.member_count, 0) as other_category_m_dest_purchasers
              FROM
                TARGET_ITEM ITEM
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT_COUPON SRC_ITEM
                    ON ITEM.qtz_item_id = SRC_ITEM.qtz_item_id
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT_COUPON SRC_S
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name = SRC_S.retail_item_category_s_name
                  LEFT JOIN SRC_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT_COUPON SRC_M
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name = SRC_M.retail_item_category_m_name
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_ITEM_COUNT_COUPON DEST_ITEM
                    ON ITEM.qtz_item_id = DEST_ITEM.qtz_item_id
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_S_COUNT_COUPON DEST_S
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_s_name = DEST_S.retail_item_category_s_name
                  LEFT JOIN DEST_MEMBER_CATEGORY_M_COUNT_COUPON DEST_M
                    ON ITEM.retail_item_category_m_name = DEST_M.retail_item_category_m_name
            )
      )
    )
      CROSS JOIN (
        SELECT
          '1'::string as purchased_from,
          '20240418'::string as contarget_pos_date_from,
          '20250417'::string as contarget_pos_date_to,
          '20240418'::string as concurrent_purchase_date_from,
          '20250417'::string as concurrent_purchase_date_to,
          'false'::string as comparison_src_flg,
          'false'::string as comparison_dest_flg,
          ''::string as src_segment_id,
          'LATEST'::string as src_segment_dt,
          ''::string as dest_segment_id,
          'LATEST'::string as dest_segment_dt,
          'ICEBOXの併買リフト＿全フレーバー②＿20240418～20250418'::string as name,
          '2025-04-18 15:00:51.821'::timestamp as extract_datetime,
          'r.tanaka@data-one.co.jp'::string as user_id,
          concat_ws(',', collect_list(retail_item_name)) as item_list,
          concat_ws(',', collect_list(qtz_item_id)) as item_id_list,
          '20250418150051821'::string as dt
        FROM
          prd_public.public.dmp_item
        WHERE
          qtz_item_id in (
            '1_1155372', '1_1440292', '1_1451189', '1_1500043', '1_1506189', '1_1453462'
          )
      )
  )
